OL,3,CHelpline for survivors of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault to close due to funding
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FA charity that supports people who
OL,8,Fhave been affected by rape and sexual
OL,9,Fviolence has announced it is closing
OL,10,Fits helpline after 14 years.
OL,12,FDevon Rape Crisis and Sexual Abuse
OL,13,FService said it is closing its phone
OL,14,Fline and email support service due to
OL,15,F"drastic" funding cuts.
OL,17,FThe service, which began in 2011, will
OL,18,Fend on 28 February 2025.
