OL,3,CHelpline for survivors of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault to close due to funding
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FIn a statement published on its
OL,8,Fwebsite, the charity said: "Despite
OL,9,Ffacing significant funding cuts of
OL,10,Faround one third for 2025-2026, Devon
OL,11,FRape Crisis and Sexual Abuse Services
OL,12,Fis excited to be purposefully moving
OL,13,Fforward to become a charity with a
OL,14,Fgreater focus on enabling survivors to
OL,15,Faccess more immediate support.
OL,17,F"However, as we face a drastic cut in
OL,18,Four proposed funding next year, we do
OL,19,Fstill need to make some really
OL,20,Fdifficult decisions to promote our
OL,21,Ffuture".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
