OL,3,CHelpline for survivors of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault to close due to funding
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe charity said 204 volunteers had
OL,8,Fstaffed the service during the past 14
OL,9,Fyears, answering more than 7,000 calls
OL,10,Fand volunteering 12,000 hours of their
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FCEO of Devon Rape Crisis and Sexual
OL,14,FAbuse Service Dr Davina Cull said the
OL,15,Fservice has been a "foundation" of the
OL,16,Fcharity, and thanked volunteers for
OL,17,Ftheir support.
OL,19,FShe said: "We are so grateful for the
OL,20,Fservice of the 204 women who have
OL,21,Fvolunteered.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
