OL,3,CHelpline for survivors of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault to close due to funding
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"We therefore celebrate this
OL,8,Fincredible achievement and ask our
OL,9,Fcommunity to show their gratitude
OL,10,Falongside us".
OL,12,FCaroline Voaden, the Liberal Democrat
OL,13,FMP for South Devon, was the former CEO
OL,14,Fof Devon Rape Crisis and said
OL,15,Finvestment in its service is vital for
OL,16,Fthe community.
OL,18,FShe said: "I'm very sad to hear that
OL,19,FDevon Rape Crisis will be closing
OL,20,Ftheir helpline due to a drop in
OL,21,Ffunding.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
