OL,3,CHelpline for survivors of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault to close due to funding
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"It's absolutely vital that support
OL,8,Fservices like this get long-term,
OL,9,Fsustainable funding instead of the
OL,10,Fpiecemeal, fragmented bits of funding
OL,11,Fcurrently on offer.
OL,13,F"It's extremely difficult to plan and
OL,14,Fdeliver services if you can only
OL,15,Fbudget for a few months ahead.
OL,17,F"Investing in survivor services means
OL,18,Fsupporting women to have better mental
OL,19,Fhealth, be able to study or work more
OL,20,Feffectively, be better parents and
OL,21,Fhave more stable relationships."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
