OL,7,FThe charity said it recommends the
OL,8,FNational Rape and Sexual Abuse
OL,9,FHelpline, which is available 24 hours
OL,10,Fa day, seven days a week, for people
OL,11,Fover the age of 16, by calling 0808
OL,12,F500 2222.
OL,14,FFor children and young people, the
OL,15,Fcharity suggested contacting
OL,16,FChildline, which is available by
OL,17,Fcalling 0800 1111.
